trans-unit.source: The abstract base class for proxies to well-known objects that were generated by the [Soapsuds Tool (Soapsuds.exe)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/40f6f8c8-b80c-4e9f-a920-31bcd0cf45c5).
trans-unit.target: A classe base abstrata para proxies com objetos conhecidos que foram gerados pelo [Soapsuds ferramenta (Soapsuds.exe)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/40f6f8c8-b80c-4e9f-a920-31bcd0cf45c5).

trans-unit.source: RemotingClientProxy provides access to the frequently used properties for Soapsuds-generated proxies that point to well-known objects (XML Web services).
trans-unit.target: RemotingClientProxy fornece acesso para as propriedades frequentemente usadas para proxies gerados Soapsuds que apontam para os objetos conhecidos (XML Web services).
